{"tid":2335440,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"禁蒙面法│湯十一：終審庭裁定合憲不意外　民主派斥剝奪權利","createTime":"2020-12-22T01:46:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T03:04:36.000Z","uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d9f1df3c95011e15485532fad050a03beb79ab4f","tid":2335440,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T01:46:06.000Z","msg":"終審法院裁定政府動用緊急法制定禁蒙面法合憲，行政會議成員湯家驊指，對結果不感意外，指個人權利不能凌駕社會整體利益或社會秩序。湯家驊在一個電台節目指，終審法院判詞逐點羅列反修例事件的暴行，以平衡測試反映個人權利不能凌駕社會整體利益，做法值得下級法院借鏡。湯家驊又指，申訴人初審勝訴時，警方已經宣佈暫緩執行《反蒙面法》，至今並無改變，而《反蒙面法》下因為公共衛生戴口罩本身是合理辯解。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2371689\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2371689&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FcdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=37322cbc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2371689</a>"},{"pid":"88af97906438277f805885cadf628fa1b22dcf7f","tid":2335440,"uid":289694,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T02:01:11.000Z","msg":"是但啦，有國安法夠晒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"885bb4923264698c2caefb2dcea41333fe5750a6","tid":2335440,"uid":288486,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T03:04:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cGLMwhP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcGLMwhP.jpg&h=eb4169db&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}